{"tid":377550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲成日搭lift都突然係某個樓層停低開門","createTime":"2017-08-27T18:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T20:35:50.000Z","uid":130358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"083b394197c113c600049e45fb0f81cc47195311","tid":377550,"uid":130358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"小弟係個公屋撚 住24樓<br />\n當我每次搭lift落街既時候<br />\n都會係18樓呢個樓層停一停 然後開門<br />\n但每次開lift時都唔會見有人入lift <br />\n咁就奇怪啦 既然開門時無人係咁會係邊個禁lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲遇過相同情況 或者可以解釋呢個現象<br />\n其實次次我都係疑住係有鬼入左liftlift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7ac7b7079146ab9c2c0584ae58248e87c14346","tid":377550,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:35:29.000Z","msg":"因為部lift壞左"},{"pid":"79ef32784adcb9b857b17c4f6d7db0e170deb4cf","tid":377550,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:37:00.000Z","msg":"有雖要先開，放心"},{"pid":"1054144245c54636420ce786ec9c1d5d742c62ae","tid":377550,"uid":130358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為部lift壞左</blockquote><br />\n但係我有個frd幢樓都係有咁既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無咁橋既！"},{"pid":"da6702ca3fb6eaeeb97b0bd561d2a15ab7307a23","tid":377550,"uid":130358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有雖要先開，放心</blockquote><br />\n盂蘭節氣魄更壯"},{"pid":"56560c37c3c2687f946c3345f731f60fdcc03861","tid":377550,"uid":16685,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:35:50.000Z","msg":"架lift唔洗抖嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji